"If you run a Mailman-based mailing list, and don't want Answerpot leeching
your list, here's how you slam the door on their sockpuppets:  Simply go to
each affected list's management page, go to the Privacy screen, and enter ^@
zeusmail.org into the banned-addresses list.  This is a wildcard regular
expression that will match any zeusmail.org address.  Then you'll probably
want to go through and delete any zeusmail.org addresses.  The easy way to
do that is ... "

Hope this helps.

